      "body" : "I figure out the problem. Is not a fetch problem, but how the <code>select</code> was made in the HQL. Try <code>SELECT emp FROM Employee emp JOIN FETCH emp.department dep</code>. JPA/Hibernate have this behaviour of return a <code>List</code> of <code>Object[]</code> when you ommit the <code>SELECT</code> part."
