  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/17431312/what-is-the-difference-between-join-and-join-fetch-when-using-jpa-and-hibernate",
  "title" : "What is the difference between JOIN and JOIN FETCH when using JPA and Hibernate",
  "body" : "<p>Please help me understand where to use a regular JOIN and where a JOIN FETCH. For example, if we have these two queries</p>\n<pre><code>FROM Employee emp\nJOIN emp.department dep\n</code></pre>\n<p>and</p>\n<pre><code>FROM Employee emp\nJOIN FETCH emp.department dep\n</code></pre>\n<p>Is there any difference between them? If yes, which one to use when?</p>\n"
